cents, which is incorrect.

781
00:31:35,550 --> 00:31:38,010
The answer is actually 5 cents.

782
00:31:38,010 --> 00:31:40,680
This is because your
thinking system one came up

783
00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,150
with the quick answer.

784
00:31:42,150 --> 00:31:44,790
Then when your system two activated,

785
00:31:44,790 --> 00:31:45,930
you started to understand

786
00:31:45,930 --> 00:31:48,180
why 5 cents was the correct answer.

787
00:31:48,180 --> 00:31:50,070
It's crucial to understand this,

788
00:31:50,070 --> 00:31:52,230
so you don't jump to conclusions

789
00:31:52,230 --> 00:31:55,701
and take on more risks than
necessary in your business.

